===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''absolute zero'''

#''(Physics)'' The coldest possible temperature, zero on the Kelvin scale, or approximately &minus;273.15 °C, &minus;459.67 °F.
# ''(Slang) ''A person or thing of absolutely no consequence.

